<h2>Contact us</h2>

<p>
  You can contact us by email at <a href="mailto:emom.sydney@gmail.com">emom.sydney@gmail.com</a> or via DM at any of our social media presences:
  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@emom.sydney">YouTube</a>,
  <a href="https://www.instagram.com/emom.sydney">Instagram</a>,
  <a href="https://www.facebook.com/EMOMsydney">Facebook</a>.
  Please allow time for a human to read and respond.
</p>

<form id="contact-us-form">
  <label for="contact-name">Name</label>
  <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" required>

  <label for="contact-email">Email</label>
  <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" required>

  <label for="contact-message">Message</label>
  <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>

  <button type="submit">Send message</button>
</form>

<script src="/assets/scripts/contact_form.js"></script>
